00:44:09,590 --> 00:44:11,110
Ang aking asawa, si Zhenzhen.

972
00:44:12,360 --> 00:44:14,070
Ako si Lu Zhenzhen,

973
00:44:14,090 --> 00:44:15,050
Mr. Ji.

974
00:44:15,630 --> 00:44:16,320
Ginang Nie.

975
00:44:17,710 --> 00:44:19,430
-Binabati kita, Ginoong Nie.
-Salamat.

976
00:44:19,430 --> 00:44:20,030
Umupo.

977
00:44:20,320 --> 00:44:21,190
Darating.

978
00:44:22,360 --> 00:44:23,610
Kumapit ka lang.

979
00:44:23,880 --> 00:44:24,710
Um...

980
00:44:25,550 --> 00:44:26,360
pasensya na po.

981
00:44:26,840 --> 00:44:28,550
Hayaan mong ipaliwanag ko sa inyong lahat.

982
00:44:28,630 --> 00:44:29,670
Sa banquet hall na ito,

983
00:44:29,670 --> 00:44:31,440
may dalawang kasalan.

984
00:44:31,550 --> 00:44:33,250
Nagpunta na lahat ang mga waiter para tumulong.

985
00:44:33,250 --> 00:44:34,480
Pero hindi mahalaga.

986
00:44:34,480 --> 00:44:36,610
Nag-ayos na ako ng attendant
mula sa aming HSKP Department.

987
00:44:36,610 --> 00:44:37,800
Malapit na siya rito.

988
00:44:37,800 --> 00:44:39,030
Gawin ang mga attendant mula sa HSKP Department

989
00:44:39,030 --> 00:44:40,690
alam mo ba ang rules ng restaurant?

990
00:44:41,840 --> 00:44:43,110
Nagtransfer ako

991
00:44:43,150 --> 00:44:45,250
ang pinakamahusay na katulong
mula sa aming executive floor.

992
00:44:45,250 --> 00:44:45,960
Mabilis siyang matuto.

993
00:44:45,960 --> 00:44:47,280
Walang magiging problema.

994
00:44:47,280 --> 00:44:48,230
Sorry talaga

995
00:44:48,230 --> 00:44:49,280
para magkagulo ka.

996
00:44:49,280 --> 00:44:50,360
Hindi naman.

997
00:44:50,590 --> 00:44:51,760
Sige. Tara kain na tayo.

998
00:44:51,760 --> 00:44:52,820
Halika na. Tara kain na tayo.

999
00:44:55,320 --> 00:44:57,510
Tanungin ang attendant-on-duty
ng executive floor na pumunta dito ngayon.

1000
00:44:57,510 --> 00:44:58,000
Bilisan mo!

